{"tid":1803123,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華為指已準備好替代 Google 方案    以印度為基地推廣鴻蒙","createTime":"2019-12-30T03:32:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T13:21:36.000Z","uid":141151,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"1ad9eb21399fe22fa1aba2de8bf6fde98fef4f2f","tid":1803123,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:32:54.000Z","msg":"華為指已準備好替代 Google 方案 以印度為基地推廣鴻蒙<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2528001/%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E6%8C%87%E5%B7%B2%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E5%A5%BD%E6%9B%BF%E4%BB%A3%20Google%20%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%20%20%E4%BB%A5%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E7%82%BA%E5%9F%BA%E5%9C%B0%E6%8E%A8%E5%BB%A3%E9%B4%BB%E8%92%99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2528001%2F%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E6%25BA%2596%25E5%2582%2599%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E6%259B%25BF%25E4%25BB%25A3%2520Google%2520%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25A1%2588%2520%2520%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%259F%25BA%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%258E%25A8%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E9%25B4%25BB%25E8%2592%2599&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkZtjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=c7ad6dc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2528001/%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E6%8C%87%E5%B7%B2%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E5%A5%BD%E6%9B%BF%E4%BB%A3%20Google%20%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%20%20%E4%BB%A5%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E7%82%BA%E5%9F%BA%E5%9C%B0%E6%8E%A8%E5%BB%A3%E9%B4%BB%E8%92%99</a><br />\n<br />\n因美國禁令，為求擺脫各種牽制，華為（Huawei）積極尋找能夠替代 Google 產品的方案。日前，華為子品牌榮耀消費者業務集團首席執行長彭博（Charles Peng）向外媒表示，華為已準備好取代 Google 的替代應用產品，將以印度作為研發基地，幫助華為在其他地區推出鴻蒙系統。<br />\n<br />\n<em>華為子品牌榮耀消費者業務集團首席執行長 Charles Peng 表示，華為已準備好取代 Google 的替代應用產品<br />\n<br />\n以印度作為研發基地，幫助華為在其他地區推出鴻蒙系統<br />\n<br />\n華為將在 12 月底準備就緒</em><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">據印度《經濟時報》（Economic Times）報道，Charles Peng 日前受訪時表示，華為正在建立自己的行動生態系統，整合至「華為行動服務」（HMS），目前已與數百家印度 App 開發商進行合作，當中包含郵件、訊息、遊戲、地圖和支付等替代 Google 的應用程序，華為將在 12 月底準備就緒，不久後就會上線。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n今年稍早時，華為宣布投入 10 億美元建立開發基金，將在中國和印度各招募 100 家 App 合作夥伴，其中印度 App 將用於印度、歐洲及其他市場，並向程式開發員開價 1.7 萬美元（約13.3萬港元）報酬，鼓勵將應用程式放上 HMS 平台。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Charles Peng 表示，消費者不會看到 Google 移動服務 GMS 跟華為的鴻蒙系統有何區別。</span></span></strong>他又指出，龐大的印度研發基地，將幫助華為在其他地區推出替代 Google 的鴻蒙系統，包括歐洲。"},{"pid":"23a580d9b2a027a4002088a2cc6aae1c1b97a258","tid":1803123,"uid":34553,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:34:06.000Z","msg":"消費者不會看到 Google 移動服務 GMS 跟華為的鴻蒙系統有何區別。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味講撚明係抄人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c977cf2f366829c45121b544ec205546aabb1276","tid":1803123,"uid":161374,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:34:20.000Z","msg":"微軟都搞唔掂，點解咁大自信"},{"pid":"eec62cc145ed54e0d1f1696b7a436baa85aa2a05","tid":1803123,"uid":166766,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"c977cf2f366829c45121b544ec205546aabb1276","tid":1803123,"uid":161374,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:34:20.000Z","msg":"微軟都搞唔掂，點解咁大自信"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:37:31.000Z","msg":"微軟係行另一個系統   華為果個  講到底都係以android 為核心 唔係重新設計  佢只係避開google 授權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faed07a39fe8134684b67b22301035c1628d40ca","tid":1803123,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:39:32.000Z","msg":"佢P30一地蟹貨無人要<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heh